'''Sandy Mokwena''' (26 Kamena 1949–24 Mutarama 2018), yari umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri serial izwi cyane ''gushyingura'' abicanyi, ''Tödliche Geschäfte'' na ''Scandal!'' . <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-01-25-tributes-pour-in-for-scandal-actor-sandy-mokwena/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 26 Kamena 1949 i Soweto, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Yashakanye na Grace Mokwena. Abashakanye bafite umukobwa umwe, Keabetswe. <ref name="timeslive">https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-01-30-sandy-mokwenas-family-we-thought-hed-recover/</ref>

Yapfuye ku ya 24 Mutarama 2018 mu gitondo azize ibintu bisanzwe afite imyaka 68. Umuhango wo gushyingura wabereye mu rusengero rwa Grace Bible i Soweto ku ya 26 Mutarama 2018. <ref>https://ewn.co.za/2018/02/02/sandy-mokwena-remembered-as-special-performer-at-funeral</ref> Nyuma yashyinguwe ahitwa Intwari Acre mu irimbi rya West Park, Johannesburg. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1972, yakinnye mu ''ikinamico Iphi Ntombi'' akina 'Cappie'. Hamwe n'ikinamico, yazengurutse ku rwego mpuzamahanga akomeza gukina kugeza mu 1984. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/Celebs/7-things-you-didnt-know-about-sandy-mokwena-20180125</ref> hanyuma muri televiziyo ''Going Up'' . <ref>https://ewn.co.za/2018/01/25/sandy-mokwena-remembered-for-his-generosity-sense-of-humour</ref>

Muri 2005, yatorewe kuba umukinnyi 'Bra Eddie Khumalo' muri opera yisabune ya televiziyo ya ''Scandal!'' . Iki gitaramo cyamenyekanye cyane aho Sandy yakomeje kugira uruhare kugeza apfuye muri 2018. Umuhango wo kwibuka wabereye kuri Scandal! sitidiyo ku wa gatatu mu rwego rwo kubahiriza imyaka 17 yamaze muri serial.  Hagati aho, yakinnye nka 'Ken Mokoena' muri serial ''Yizo Yizo 1'' . <ref>https://ewn.co.za/2018/01/25/actor-sandy-mokwena-dies</ref>

Usibye ''Scandal!'', Yatanze ibiganiro byinshi kuri tereviziyo nka ''Generations'', ''Khululeka'', ''Soul City'', ''Ubutabera kuri Bose'' na ''Tolerance Zero'' . <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-01-25-breaking-scandal-actor-sandy-mokoena-aka-bra-eddie-has-died/</ref> <ref>https://northcoastcourier.co.za/lnn/352765/breaking-popular-scandal-actor-sandy-mokwena-dies/</ref> Hagati aho, yakoraga muri filime: ''Taxi to Soweto'' (1992), ''The Principal'' (1996), ''Dead End'' (1999) and ''Scarback'' (2000) <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=3726</ref>

